{"tid":1958271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"半年前仲係一個手足 半年後就係一個五毛","createTime":"2020-04-04T13:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T01:46:40.000Z","uid":79793,"like":17,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef98346c247b32c124597ce6435394be7181e0b","tid":1958271,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"半年前叫大家出黎唱不屈進行曲提升士氣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人自殺就老閪都屈佢係狗做先，完全冇獨立思考，同藍絲一樣<br />\n<br />\n另外有手足被捕就好嬲好嬲，個個都想無成本抗爭<br />\n<br />\n自從不分化不割席唔好鬥黃出現左之後，慢慢大家發現冇成本抗爭先係真理，反正被捕果個又唔會係自己，有唔啱聽嘅野就屈佢係三毛係狗係阿蛇，永遠都唔識醒，想問下嬲係唔係可以光復香港？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jfOFZ3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jfOFZ3.gif&h=5e53010c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收到風上面話要冷處理呢首歌！唔可以比好多人唱呢首歌！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1762003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1762003</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc5496849d10275e3270f972f46e62da4ee52cf5","tid":1958271,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"大家繼續好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93d5f6ef0c31fd7f40b6026135b903ff44b0086","tid":1958271,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:34:11.000Z","msg":"顧家豪二五仔出賣屠龍小隊 92籤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1958261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1958261</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2d4684bb419ee4053dc6f1b591b238898bb33591","tid":1958271,"uid":328890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:38:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84eb9ad5fc6823389c355f8064f581f398af0ee4","tid":1958271,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"麻煩師兄借一借個位<br />\n可唔可以入一入嚟幫幫本土議員撇除選舉不利因素,避免立法會選舉時到時發生優先老人同限制點票人數情況<br />\n<a href=\"https: